courseName: Riyad as-Salihin Explained with Shaykh Dr Tarek Elgawhary

courseDescription: This course is an introductory Theology (Aqidah) course in Islamic Creed. The course uses “Ascent to Felicity” by Imam Abu al-Ikhlas al-Shurumbulali (may Allah have mercy on him), translated by Sh. Faraz A. Khan.
